00:44:01,120 --> 00:44:02,240
Some of you might be familiar

1300
00:44:02,240 --> 00:44:03,600
with my video about Bloodborne.

1301
00:44:03,600 --> 00:44:05,360
It kinda revolutionized

1302
00:44:05,360 --> 00:44:07,680
the face of game design for all time.

1303
00:44:07,680 --> 00:44:08,240
Just kidding.

1304
00:44:08,240 --> 00:44:10,320
But it did kind of invent a newish concept,

1305
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:11,280
at least I think it does.

1306
00:44:11,280 --> 00:44:13,040
I haven't heard anyone else using it before,

1307
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:14,400
called play conditioning,

1308
